WITH ActorMovies AS (
    SELECT 
        ak.name AS actor_name,
        ak.person_id AS actor_id,
        ti.title AS movie_title,
        ti.production_year AS movie_year,
        COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS co_stars_count
    FROM 
        aka_name ak
    JOIN 
        cast_info c ON ak.person_id = c.person_id
    JOIN 
        title ti ON c.movie_id = ti.id
    GROUP BY 
        ak.name, ak.person_id, ti.title, ti.production_year
),
ActorCoStarStats AS (
    SELECT 
        actor_name,
        movie_title,
        movie_year,
        AVG(co_stars_count) AS avg_co_stars,
        COUNT(*) AS movie_count
    FROM 
        ActorMovies
    GROUP BY 
        actor_name, movie_title, movie_year
),
TopActors AS (
    SELECT 
        actor_name,
        AVG(avg_co_stars) AS avg_co_stars_over_all_movies
    FROM 
        ActorCoStarStats
    GROUP BY 
        actor_name
    ORDER BY 
        avg_co_stars_over_all_movies DESC
    LIMIT 10
)

SELECT 
    ta.actor_name,
    ta.avg_co_stars_over_all_movies,
    COUNT(DISTINCT tm.movie_title) AS total_movies,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT tm.movie_title, ', ') AS movie_titles
FROM 
    TopActors ta
JOIN 
    ActorCoStarStats tm ON ta.actor_name = tm.actor_name
GROUP BY 
    ta.actor_name, ta.avg_co_stars_over_all_movies
ORDER BY 
    total_movies DESC

GROUP BY "aka_name0"."name", "aka_name0"."person_id", "title0"."title", "title0"."production_year") AS "t9"

SELECT COALESCE("t13"."ACTOR_NAME", "t13"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t13"."AVG_CO_STARS_OVER_ALL_MOVIES", "t13"."TOTAL_MOVIES", "t13"."MOVIE_TITLES"
FROM (SELECT "t6"."ACTOR_NAME", "t6"."AVG_CO_STARS_OVER_ALL_MOVIES", COUNT(DISTINCT "t10"."MOVIE_TITLE") AS "TOTAL_MOVIES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t10"."MOVIE_TITLE", ', ') AS "MOVIE_TITLES"
FROM (SELECT "ACTOR_NAME", AVG("AVG_CO_STARS") AS "AVG_CO_STARS_OVER_ALL_MOVIES"
FROM (SELECT "t2"."ACTOR_NAME", AVG("t2"."CO_STARS_COUNT") AS "AVG_CO_STARS"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("title0"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("title0"."production_year") AS "MOVIE_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."id") AS "CO_STARS_COUNT"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" AS "title0" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title0"."id"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."person_id", "title0"."title", "title0"."production_year") AS "t2"
GROUP BY "t2"."ACTOR_NAME", "t2"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t2"."MOVIE_YEAR") AS "t4"
GROUP BY "ACTOR_NAME"
ORDER BY 2 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t6"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "t9"."ACTOR_NAME", "t9"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t9"."MOVIE_YEAR", AVG("t9"."CO_STARS_COUNT") AS "AVG_CO_STARS", COUNT(*) AS "MOVIE_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_name0"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("s1"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("s1"."production_year") AS "MOVIE_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info0"."id") AS "CO_STARS_COUNT"
FROM "aka_name" AS "aka_name0"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" AS "cast_info0" ON "aka_name0"."person_id" = "cast_info0"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info0"."movie_id" = "s1"."id"
GROUP BY "aka_name0"."name", "aka_name0"."person_id", "s1"."title", "s1"."production_year") AS "t9"
GROUP BY "t9"."ACTOR_NAME", "t9"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t9"."MOVIE_YEAR") AS "t10" ON "t6"."ACTOR_NAME" = "t10"."ACTOR_NAME"
GROUP BY "t6"."ACTOR_NAME", "t6"."AVG_CO_STARS_OVER_ALL_MOVIES"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t13"
